title: What Did We Learn From Bucks-Heat
description:
Jalen & Jacoby dive into Milwaukee's win over the Miami Mafia - what did we learn?! Plus, Philly might have a Big 3 of their own, Zion's latest health update isn't great, and KD returns to night to save the Nets. And in the Podcast Exclusive, Jalen asks the quintessential question of our time: "Since when is 8 inches not enough?" It's about QB hands, folks. Relax. Tap in!
